---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="Privacy Policy" description="Hartzog.ai privacy policy — how we handle your data.">
  <article class="prose">
    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><em>Last updated: {new Date().toLocaleDateString('en-US', { year: 'numeric', month: 'long', day: 'numeric' })}</em></p>

    <h2>Overview</h2>
    <p>
      Hartzog.ai ("we", "us", "our") respects your privacy. This policy explains what
      data we collect, how we use it, and your rights regarding that data.
    </p>

    <h2>Data We Collect</h2>
    <h3>Information You Provide</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Contact form submissions</strong> — name, email, message content</li>
      <li><strong>Newsletter signups</strong> — email address</li>
    </ul>

    <h3>Automatically Collected</h3>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>Analytics data</strong> — page views, referrer, country (no personal identifiers).
        We use privacy-focused analytics that do not use cookies or track individuals.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How We Use Your Data</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>To respond to your inquiries</li>
      <li>To send newsletters you subscribed to</li>
      <li>To understand aggregate site usage and improve our content</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Third-Party Services</h2>
    <p>We use the following third-party services:</p>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>GitHub Pages</strong> — hosting (GitHub's <a href="https://docs.github.com/en/site-policy/privacy-policies/github-general-privacy-statement">privacy statement</a>)</li>
      <li><strong>Formspree</strong> — form processing (processes contact form and newsletter submissions)</li>
      <li><strong>Plausible Analytics</strong> — privacy-focused analytics (no cookies, no personal data)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Cookies</h2>
    <p>
      This site does not use cookies for tracking. No cookie consent banner is required.
    </p>

    <h2>Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You may:</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Request a copy of data we hold about you</li>
      <li>Request deletion of your data</li>
      <li>Unsubscribe from newsletters at any time</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>Contact</h2>
    <p>
      For privacy-related questions, contact us at
      <a href="mailto:contact@hartzog.dev">contact@hartzog.dev</a> or via our
      <a href="/contact">contact form</a>.
    </p>
  </article>
</BaseLayout>
